---
source: crates/markdown-neuraxis-syntax/src/lib.rs
expression: "insta_format_tree(&tree, 0)"
---
ROOT@0..31
  UNORDERED_LIST@0..31
    LIST_ITEM@0..31
      DASH@0..1 "-"
      WHITESPACE@1..2 " "
      PARAGRAPH@2..9
        TEXT@2..8 "Parent"
        NEWLINE@8..9 "\\n"
      WHITESPACE@9..10 "\t"
      UNORDERED_LIST@10..31
        LIST_ITEM@10..31
          DASH@10..11 "-"
          WHITESPACE@11..12 " "
          PARAGRAPH@12..31
            TEXT@12..15 "Tab"
            DASH@15..16 "-"
            TEXT@16..24 "indented"
            WHITESPACE@24..25 " "
            TEXT@25..30 "child"
            NEWLINE@30..31 "\\n"
